{
  "texts": [
    "Similar to i2b2-2012, this task is also framed as NER with 22 labels.",
    "Figure 2 shows some examples taken from the training subset of the dataset.",
    "The ISARIC COVID-19 Clinical Database e consists of data from patients hospitalised with COVID-19 who are enrolled in an ISARIC Partner clinical study (Garcia-Gallo et al. 2022).",
    "The data (which are standardised to CDISC STDM format f) include hospital admission and discharge records, signs and symptoms, comorbidities, vital signs, treatments and outcomes.",
    "Nonprespecified terms related to one of five categories; medical history, complications, signs and symptoms, new diagnosis at follow-up or category not recorded."
  ]
}